precis:
Amendment to the SPECIAL SERVICES AND FEES REGULATIONS revoking the
provisions Collect on Delivery Service (C.O.D.) and Special Delivery
Service and modifying a reference in the rates table respecting money
packets to allow Canada Post Corporation to establish the rates of postage
for that product outside regulations.
